on the goddamn moon.

02:28.916 --> 02:30.333
Ha! And what am I doing?

02:30.333 --> 02:33.833
Well, the next scene, you teach a child
about tolerance through the power of song,

02:33.833 --> 02:36.083
which apparently makes a nun horny.

02:36.083 --> 02:38.291
