02:44.291 --> 02:46.458
Oh, bullshit? This is not bullshit.

02:46.458 --> 02:48.833
This is a giant moment in history.

02:48.833 --> 02:52.125
You know it. Right up there
with your comeback TV special.

02:52.125 --> 02:53.125
Arguably.

02:54.833 --> 02:57.250
Hey. You promised me you'd quit that shit.

02:59.083 --> 03:03.083
