05:37.625 --> 05:38.958
- Not remotely.
- All right.

05:38.958 --> 05:41.708
So, uh, you want a star map or what?

05:41.708 --> 05:45.083
Five buck extra gets you
Paul Newman's gate code.

05:45.083 --> 05:47.208
Tell you what, Flyboy.

05:47.208 --> 05:50.291
I'm a lot more interested
in that other shit you're selling.

05:50.291 --> 05:52.125
- Know what I mean?
- Ah.

05:52.125 --> 05:53.958
Right, right, right. Yeah.

05:53.958 --> 05:55.708
Check it out.

05:55.708 --> 05:57.583
So, tell me, Flyboy,

05:57.583 --> 06:00.416
