how come you're dressed like a pimp?

06:00.416 --> 06:03.291
Okay. Yeah, well,
I mean, there is some overlap.

06:03.291 --> 06:05.500
But come on,
you want some of this coke or not?

06:05.500 --> 06:07.458
More like all of it.

06:07.458 --> 06:09.208
All of it? Oh.

06:09.708 --> 06:10.958
Oh!

06:10.958 --> 06:14.250
Well, guess who's
an official fucking Elvis fan!

06:14.250 --> 06:15.708
Right on, man!

06:15.708 --> 06:16.791
All right. All right.

06:16.791 --> 06:19.541
Now, um, I don't normally
deal in bulk, but I--

06:19.541 --> 06:20.791
- Shut up.
- Uh, done.

06:20.791 --> 06:24.416
Now, ordinarily, I'd just kick your ass
for being a piece-of-shit drug dealer

06:24.416 --> 06:26.958
