without being noticed.

06:45.166 --> 06:47.708
So, I'll need to borrow a few things.

06:50.791 --> 06:55.250
Wow, that actually looks way better
on you than it did on me, honestly.

06:55.250 --> 06:57.750
Yeah, like nobody saw that coming.

07:03.625 --> 07:06.625
<i>Mission Control awaits word. The lunar--</i>

07:07.708 --> 07:09.625
<i>What are you doing, Agent Ryder?</i>

07:09.625 --> 07:10.833
