07:39.125 --> 07:40.416
Turns out I do.

07:40.958 --> 07:44.666
Okay. E, but baby,
whatever you do, don't hurt the coat.

07:45.958 --> 07:47.125
I actually get that.

07:55.291 --> 07:57.166
Paging Dr. John Carpenter.

07:57.166 --> 07:59.041
Damn it!

07:59.041 --> 08:00.750
Uh, shouldn't you be making a movie now?

08:00.750 --> 08:02.583
All right, look,
just cut the shit, will you?

08:02.583 --> 08:05.208
- What are you really up to?
- Oh my God, paranoid. Nothing.

08:05.208 --> 08:07.125
- Where's the trust?
- Irradiated.

08:07.125 --> 08:09.875
