08:31.083 --> 08:33.208
- You got mustard on your face.
- Yes, I know.

08:33.208 --> 08:36.125
You good with that?
Walking around with mustard on your face?

08:36.125 --> 08:38.750
Oh shit! Dr. Carpenter carries a gun?

08:38.750 --> 08:40.541
Ooh! Plot twist.

08:40.541 --> 08:42.250
Whoa, whoa, wait. What's the line again?

08:42.250 --> 08:45.208
Your line is, "Yes." Fucking dipshit.

08:48.541 --> 08:49.500
Night vision.

08:50.500 --> 08:53.125
Oh shit. Goddamn it.

08:53.125 --> 08:56.625
